  "notes": "Quill \u2014 the Scholar specialty. Cool neutral teal/parchment palette, low glow, very low surprise reactivity, very high curiosity, long sleep threshold. Built to sit and read for hours. Best fit for research assistant, document-summarizer, citation-checker agents. Suggested Eleven voice style: measured tenor/alto, bookish clarity; think audiobook narrator for nonfiction."
